                                "text": "Lots of interesting ideas in this piece. I was confused about what makes the language computational, and it helped me to think of it as a language in an environment. Which includes the built-in functions, all the data definitions that come with, etc.\n\nIt does make me think of the promise and tragedy of the semantic web and Wikidata, which feels like it could offer a foundation for an open version of something like this."
